Accelerator-Z was designed to support all community related efforts including support, chat moderation, channel curation and so on.

@SigliZNN is literally one of the pillars of this community, an invaluable member and a green ray of hope for everyone in darker times, devoted to this project since the very beginning of this entire journey.

I've encouraged him to make proposals and proceed requesting monthly funds from AZ in order to sustain himself and continue delivering for this amazing community.
